# Generated Dart/Flutter artifacts. None of these are source; all are
# reproduced by `pub get`, `build_runner`, or `dart doc`. Patterns without
# a leading slash match at any depth, so they also cover example/.

# Tool and build caches.
.dart_tool/
build/
**/doc/api/

# Library lockfile. workbench_shell is a published package, not an app:
# it must resolve against a range of consumer versions, so pinning its own
# lockfile gives false confidence and has no effect on consumers.
# See https://dart.dev/tools/pub/private-files#pubspeclock.
/pubspec.lock

# OS and editor noise.
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.iml
.idea/

# Symphonize/conduct local progress scratch — never commit.
*.local.md
